{"tid":356753,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"頭一年有憧景，第二年好難頂，第三年黎緊","createTime":"2017-08-12T10:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T17:15:04.000Z","uid":134627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8df7b38a241e62183ca2fea48468e3643e856f18","tid":356753,"uid":134627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"當你畢業搵到第一份工<br />\n個個讚你好野<br />\n自己都有少少自豪感<br />\n努力做虛心學 <br />\n第一年 過了<br />\n<br />\n第二年 開始發現做緊既野好悶啦<br />\n就開始諗份工係咪岩自己做呢<br />\n做既野重複同悶<br />\n日日坐係到 近視又深 下身又肥<br />\n開始好負面<br />\n無左第一年既感覺<br />\n<br />\n但無奈又走唔出個comfort zone <br />\n屋企排行最大<br />\n唔到你話走就走<br />\n<br />\n黎緊第三年啦<br />\n<br />\n點捱下去<br />\n<br />\n有無人有經驗可以分享下<br />\n心態如何調整<br />\n<br />\n謝"},{"pid":"828dc873ffbff26ab63f40aa075a4a11029688b4","tid":356753,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:46:30.000Z","msg":"咪轉工囉"},{"pid":"eadbc15b7a21b8af9e0236c1f92c29d6b6d041a3","tid":356753,"uid":134627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪轉工囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由頭黎過 搵唔番咁既人工啦"},{"pid":"31dea9947da50151d567690c6cfc157a999ee0ff","tid":356753,"uid":11437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"邊行幾歲？"},{"pid":"737a9bb52bdcf2df51efe4b6905d42d77fcb1d33","tid":356753,"uid":123524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊行幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n似係 audit"},{"pid":"30562d3a80e51474ca35a9495d001c5980eafd7d","tid":356753,"uid":134627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊行幾歲？</blockquote>surveyor 26"}]}